flowchart TD
    A["POST /api/agents/run/stream\nsrc/backend/routers/agent.py::runtime_agent_run_stream"] -->|"Trigger: client submits RuntimeAgentRunRequest"| B["services.agent_service::stream_runtime_agent"]

    B -->|"1) _get_or_compile_stream_runtime()\nData: process cache handle\nWhy: avoid per-request runtime compile"| C["Compiled runtime cache\n(_STREAM_RUNTIME_CACHE)"]
    C -->|"Cache miss -> _compile_stream_runtime() once/process\nData: _ScaffoldCompiledStreamRuntime"| D["Runtime adapter with astream + ainvoke"]

    B -->|"2) Emit heartbeat\nsequence=1 event=heartbeat\nData: query + started status\nWhy: immediate liveness"| E["SSE client stream"]

    B -->|"3) runtime.astream(payload, db, tracing)\nTrigger function: _await_runtime_call(...)"| F["Runtime stream events"]
    F -->|"If events exist: map each to RuntimeAgentStreamEvent\nData: event/data only (sequence normalized)"| E

    B -->|"4) runtime.ainvoke(payload, db, tracing)\nTrigger function: _await_runtime_call(...)"| G["RuntimeAgentRunResponse"]

    B -->|"Fallback branch when astream yields none\nEmit sequence+1 event=progress\nData: step=invoke_fallback"| E
    B -->|"Emit sub_queries from ainvoke result\nData: sub_queries + count"| E
    B -->|"Emit completed from ainvoke result\nData: agent_name/output/thread_id/checkpoint_id/tool_assignments\nWhy: stable completion contract"| E

    H["Decision: always call ainvoke even when astream runs\nTradeoff: one deterministic completion source, extra runtime call in scaffold mode"] -.-> B
    I["Decision: fallback excludes logging-state payloads\nTradeoff: simpler deterministic contract for current UI/tests"] -.-> B
